How much crypto you need to buy the most expensive cars

Cars is one of the favorite toys that we all love to drive, if you want a moving house, a bus is the best option or if you want to drive in the desert, go for a sandrail. But in our daily lives we love to have comfort, style and uniqueness in our vehicle.

Some of the most expensive car ensuring luxury, style and comfort at the same time have been developed by major automakers around the world including Ferrari, BMW, Audi, Porsche, Bugatti and others. Such luxury and style comes with a cost of up to millions of dollars.

The most expensive car in our list down below is Bughatti Divo with a cost of upto $6 million or 165.3 btc. It’s a beautiful car designed by bughatti with only 40 copies available in the market. The pre-requisite to own a bughatti divo is to first buy a $3 million Bugatti Chiron, so this already confirms the car to be only available for the filthy rich.
